## 水平柱状图

```python
def barh(
    y: float | ArrayLike,
    width: float | ArrayLike,
    height: float | ArrayLike = 0.8,
    left: float | ArrayLike | None = None,
    *,
    align: Literal["center", "edge"] = "center",
    data=None,
    **kwargs,
)
```